Class Floor

  • java.lang.Object
    • Cell
      • Floor

  • public class Floor
extends Cell
    Characters will collect any Collectables on a floor tile they move on if there is one. The Floor class is a subclass of the Cell class.
    Creation Date: 20/11/19.
    Last Modification Date: 6/12/19.
    Version:
    2.2
    Author:
    Timothy Roger (977422), Nihal Goindi (976005)
